title: Rod Argent Moving Home
description:
Rod Argents' solo album,"Moving Home" plus the a & b side of the single "Gymnopedies No1  & Light Fantastic. 

NOTE: Tracks 11 & 12 are from 7" 45rpm vinyl, and have all the hiss, clicks & pops you get with a 30 year old piece of vinyl.

The album features such luminaries as Gary Moore, Alphonso Johnson, Phill Collins, Morris Pert, Jack Lancaster & Clive Chapman, and was produced by Robin Lumley.
